summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2014 SUBARU OUTBACK. THE CONTACT STATED THAT NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 19V009000 (AIR BAGS) EXCEEDED A REASONABLE AMOUNT OF TIME FOR REPAIR. THE CONTACT RECEIVED THE RECALL NOTIFICATION ON MARCH 11, 2019. THE CONTACT SPOKE WITH AN UNKNOWN SUBARU DEALER WHO STATED THAT THEY WERE ONLY SERVICING ONE VEHICLE PER DAY. THE CONTACT WOULD HAVE TO WAIT UNTIL AUGUST OF 2019 TO HAVE THE VEHICLE REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT CONTACTED. THE CONTACT HAD NOT EXPERIENCED A FAILURE.
